{"tid":2134443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［有線中國組，有片］蝗蟲湧至 雲南不見天日 當局稱已受控 8月或再爆","createTime":"2020-07-31T17:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T20:15:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a63fa2edf2649133fffae1a41323ae26aaf50c74","tid":2134443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/615380899112667/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F615380899112667%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252Fcablechinadesk%252F%26_rdr&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzORVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=2f0f664b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/615380899112667/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n一到6月，大量的黃脊竹蝗從老撾越境飛到雲南。在普洱江城縣，大批黃脊竹蝗在此「落地生根」，蠶食農作物，已經波及超過14萬畝農田。<br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲為患，當地的林葉部門，出動無人機，在農田的上空噴灑殺蟲劑。此外，當局亦建立了由多個省市聯合組成的，24小時蝗災監測網絡。<br />\n<br />\n負責黃脊竹蝗防治工作的魏大嵩就說：「我們從7月20日開始，集中人力物力就在這裡進行防治。通過防治以後，黃脊竹蝗每天都在死亡。通過我們有效防治，黃脊竹蝗密度大量減少，之前一到下午四、五點是遮天蔽日的，但是從昨天(28日)開始，這個黃脊竹蝗已經看不見在天上飛了。」<br />\n<br />\n當局指黃脊竹蝗災害已經受控，而且有放緩的趨勢。但有專家分析，到了8月，雲南邊境會迎來第二波的黃脊竹蝗，好大機會再次大規模爆發蝗災。如果不及時堵截黃脊竹蝗擴散，未來好可能會變成常態。<br />\n<br />\n#雲南<br />\n#黃脊竹蝗<br />\n#可控可防<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"0cead17a99053eecd82369d697d9ce98bc5adc57","tid":2134443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"【北斗導航系統應用廣泛】<br />\n【記者實測：巴士比預計遲7分鐘到站】<br />\n【學者：中國全球定位不求人 軍事上更獨立自主】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/315981779527605/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F615380899112667%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F315981779527605%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252Fcablechinadesk%252Fvideos%252F615380899112667%252F%26_rdr&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzORVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=ce67b6a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/315981779527605/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F615380899112667%2F&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"019a2c78fe5c63ec7b0ce79e20c0342ee16db47a","tid":2134443,"uid":25525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"有線造謠犯國安法"},{"pid":"b58fcd1be178a8886c89e7fa9a3d37c607a39d5a","tid":2134443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣劇情<br />\n<br />\n【武漢護士墮樓身亡】<br />\n【曾組織罷工反抗上司遭針對】<br />\n【生前閉路電視片段已損毀】<br />\n<br />\n周三早上10時45分，武漢協和醫院一名心血管內科護士，於內科一號樓墮樓，搶救後不治身亡。墮樓現場在當日下午清理乾淨，有警員到心血管內科病房調查，家屬對於突如其來的噩耗都難以接受。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/633467190708859/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F633467190708859%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252Fcablechinadesk%252F%26_rdr&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzORVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=33caa725\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/633467190708859/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"89b21aa31b00464d1443fd761f8ea18b4da72d7b","tid":2134443,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019a2c78fe5c63ec7b0ce79e20c0342ee16db47a","tid":2134443,"uid":25525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"有線造謠犯國安法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d214bb4259c1a2ac517e2aeb80f834493a6397b","tid":2134443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20